ygData.subject: Planar Travel - opinions, tips, strategies
ygData.msgSnippet: These lists have been dead for too long, so in an attempt to spur some discussion here, and because I ll be venturing into the Plane of Hate and Fear very soon
ygData.messageBody:
These lists have been dead for too long, so in an attempt to spur some
discussion here, and because I'll be venturing into the Plane of Hate and
Fear very soon with my DE SK, I would like to hear opinions, tips and
strategies from those who do plane trips on a regular basis.

Some of the things mentioned by various high level players on my server, is
that they use alternate equipment in the case they can not return to recover
their corpses (IE - use combine weapons and banded armor for instance). Any
information that anyone would be willing to share, would be much
appreciated. I anticipate hearing what you all have to say/share!
